<br>
So, I honestly doubt these 6 people would all find a class they enjoyed from the first attempt.<br>
<br>
However, my suggestion would be:<br>
Paladin<br>
Cleric<br>
Enchanter<br>
Bard<br>
Rogue<br>
Mage<br>
<br>
You have all the basics covered plus 2 forms of mana regen and 2 classes that can heal.<br>
<br>
If they don't have PoP, I'd suggest a Wizard/Druid in place of the Magician just so they have easier access to moving around.<br>
<br>
If they aren't planning on getting very high very fast, any groups do well below 55 as long as they have a healer. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://members.aol.com/nodnarbjh/csig.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
