<br>
Those people suggestion all pet caster type groups are giving really poor answers imo.  While most pet heavy groups make nice xp combinations, they are lacking in several areas.  If you have 4-5 mages in a group, well gearing them is a pain cause you need so much int caster stuff, the game becomes very 1 dimensional as you have virtually no utility since everyone can do the same thing as everyone else in the group, you never learn strengths, weakness of other classes, etc.  You will most likely be lacking in the travel department (no soe/sow/ports,etc), possibly no rez, etc.<br>
<br>
If I had to start a group of 6 i'd probably want:<br>
enchanter (slow + haste + mana regen + tash + mana drain)<br>
druid (backup heals + evac + nukes + travel)<br>
cleric (main healer + buffs + rez)<br>
warrior (main tank)<br>
sk (puller + off tank + summon corpse)<br>
mage (damage + debuff)<br>
<br>
The only thing that can stop this group is locked doors <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showMessageRange?topicID=8097.topic&start=21&stop=31>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showPrevMessage?topicID=8097.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showNextMessage?topicID=8097.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8097.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.threadControl?topicID=8097.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=8097.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=8097.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub102.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="themagicianstowergeneral">General<option value="themagicianstowerfrm32">Class Balance<option value="themagicianstowe